						<summary>

						<p>Chōḻa, Rājarāja III (?), 3rd year = A.D. 1219.</p>						

						<p>This is a resolution by the <hi rend="italic">nāṭṭār</hi> of Panaṅgāḍu-nāḍu that they would not harm anybody in the fields or on the highways in Ambaṉavar-Nalvayalūr and if they did so they would incur a penalty of one <hi rend="italic">mā</hi> of land to the temple.</p>						

						<p>[Published in <hi rend="italic">IPS</hi>, No. 186.]</p>						

